'''Abolfadl Harawi''' ({{lang-fa|ابو الفضل هروى}}) was a 10th-century [[astronomer]] from [[Rey, Iran|Rey]], [[Iran|Persia]] who, along with [[al-Khujandi]], studied under the patronage of the [[Buyid]] dynasty.

