{{Birds by population sidebar}} This is a '''list of [[Galliformes]] species by global population'''. While numbers are estimates, they have been made by the experts in their fields. For more information on how these estimates were ascertained, see Wikipedia's articles on [[population biology]] and [[population ecology]].
This list is not comprehensive, as not all Galliformes have had their numbers quantified. {{-}}
